OL,5,G1730 The Directors
OL,6,     FStanley Kubrick is considered one
OL,7,     Fof the greatest and most
OL,8,     Finfluential directors in cinematic
OL,9,     Fhistory. His cinematic masterpiece
OL,10,     Fwas to arrive in 1968 with the
OL,11,     Fcreation of 2001: A Space Odyssey.
